{"tid":686427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[廢老FatFat]社署將於下周一(4日)向36萬名「高額長者生活津貼」發放約1萬元","createTime":"2018-06-01T08:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T05:15:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0222327db5646867481ab411cb561a47fa2a588","tid":686427,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:45:12.000Z","msg":"津貼額每月達3485港元的「高額長者生活津貼」今日(1日)正式實施，並展開第三階段「新申請」程序，供未有領取普通長者生活津貼、高齡津貼或傷殘津貼的65歲或以上長者申請。合資格長者只要在今年內提交申請及符合條件，包括年齡、居港、入息及資產規定，即可獲發由生效日期(即去年5月1日)或合資格日期起計一筆過款項，故此亦毋須急於申請初期提交申請。<br />\n<br />\n若長者的入息及或資產超過高額長生津規定限額，但符合普通長生津的規定限額，可考慮申領普通長生津，但上述一筆過追溯款項安排並不適用於普通長生津。另外，社署<span style=\"color: red;\">將於下周一(4日)向約36萬名第一階段「自動轉換」安排下，合資格領取高額長生津的長者，發放一筆過約1萬港元款項</span>，存入其長生津銀行戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180601/bkn-20180601111242075-0601_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180601%2Fbkn-20180601111242075-0601_00822_001.html&d=Qe4kh0FQtnTlaK23Hw01o2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=4e77724f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180601/bkn-20180601111242075-0601_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"42b449743e8d6af08bef468461574e05828af03f","tid":686427,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"很想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e864a78cc9c4fd74396952036e6335fe5e62a893","tid":686427,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"又咪係畀廢老拎去益閪洋菜街啲老雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1338064e59bbe8356bbede2fd03acc9a3e70c1fb","tid":686